<div class="row top-buffer">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h2>Careers site support</h2>

        <p><a href="/help" ms.title="Need general help? Visit our help center">Need general help? Visit our help center</a></p>

        <p>You've got questions, we've got answers.</p>

        <p><a href="https://aka.ms/accommodationrequest"  target="_blank" ms.title="Need help with apply? Request an accommodation">Need help with apply? Request an accommodation</a></p>
        <p>If you need an accommodation during the application process, such as our web page not working with your assistive technology, let us know and we will make sure you get the help you need.</p>

        <p><a href="https://aka.ms/gcs-support"  target="_blank" ms.title="Need a response? Open a support request">Need a response? Open a support request</a></p>
        <p>Drop us a line - we are happy to help.</p>

        <h2>Other support options</h2>

        <p>Microsoft offers online resources to help you get the most out of your Microsoft products.</p>

        <p><a href="http://support.microsoft.com/answerdesk/accessibility" target="_blank" ms.title="Disability Answer Desk">Disability Answer Desk</a></p>
        <p>Disability Answer Desk agents assist customers with disabilities, including people with blindness, low vision, hearing loss, or other impairments.</p>

        <p><a href="http://windows.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/tutorial" target="_blank" ms.title="Getting Started with Windows">Getting Started with Windows</a></p>
        <p>Information on Windows operating system, including a product tutorial and information on new features.</p>

        <p><a href="http://answers.microsoft.com/" target="_blank" ms.title="Microsoft Community">Microsoft Community</a></p>
        <p>Get assistance from the Microsoft Community.</p>

        <p><a href="http://support.microsoft.com/" target="_blank" ms.title="Microsoft Support">Microsoft Support</a></p>
        <p>Self-help guides and other online resources.</p>



